# Product Overview

This is an NGO (Non-Governmental Organization) web platform built with Laravel. The application appears to be designed to connect volunteers with NGOs and facilitate donations.

## Key Features
- NGO directory and exploration
- Volunteer registration and management
- Contact and information pages
- Admin panel for content management
- Blog functionality
- Team and resource pages
- TVET (Technical and Vocational Education and Training) programs

## Target Users
- NGOs looking to showcase their work
- Volunteers seeking opportunities
- Donors wanting to contribute to causes
- Administrators managing the platform

The platform serves as a bridge between charitable organizations and people who want to help through volunteering or donations.